    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the [INAUDIBLE] was-- we-- we had to slip in the middle of the night to walk, and we were-- just like they will come and they will get you.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
